    <div class="case-study__content-wrapper--md grid--centered-sm" data-aos="fade-up">
      <p>To back up the imagine if statement, we then show them why they should care about the cause, what they are supporting, and why they should trust this solution. We wanted to design the Fund in a way that would be engaging to read through, but wouldn’t be so dense as to turn off the emotional reasons that attracts someone to give.</p>
    </div>

